data.description: Location, location, location!  Don’t miss out on this beautiful home located just off Pace Patriot Boulevard in the Tiburon West neighborhood.  Just a short walk to Pace High School, S.S Dixon Elementary, Pace library and convenient shopping on Highway 90! The fire and Sheriffs department are just around the corner for peace of mind.  The home has a well-maintained front yard with attractive landscaping. The large covered front porch is perfect for rocking chairs to enjoy the sunrise and your morning cup of coffee. The home is move-in ready with pleasant paint colors throughout, The front door opens to a large entryway perfect for welcoming guests. The guest bath has luxury vinyl flooring, tub and shower combination.  The Master bath has luxury vinyl flooring, new his and her vanities, a separate shower and a large bathtub to soak away the stress of the day. The walk-in master closet has laminate flooring and plenty of space for all your clothes.  The main living area and kitchen has easy to maintain tile. New carpeting is scheduled to be installed in the three bedrooms. The bonus room which is currently the office/music room has a closet, wood laminate flooring and beautiful custom barn door, could be a 4th bedroom if needed for your guest or a larger family.. The living area has tall, vaulted ceilings. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, pantry, breakfast nook and plenty of counter space for meal prep.  Your guests can pull up a stool at the bar while you do your magic in the kitchen. The fenced backyard has a screened-in porch as well as an open-air patio perfect for grilling or enjoying the quiet wooded area behind the fence. Make an appointment to see this home soon because it won’t last long!
